    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! I\u2019ve got something truly special for you today. This isn't just a car; it's been my absolute pride and joy. It\u2019s in such incredible shape that it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014honestly, photos don't do this beauty justice! I\u2019ve babied it from day one, keeping it tucked away and meticulously cared for. You might find a tiny character mark if you really go looking with a magnifying glass, but to any enthusiast, she\u2019s a total knockout. I'm only letting her go to make room for a new project, and I'd love to see it go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come by, let's grab a coffee, and you can see for yourself!",
