      "description": "Offering a concours-level specimen that redefines the 'mint' standard. This chassis has been maintained with zero regard for cost, featuring a blueprinted powertrain that delivers linear power delivery across the entire rev range. The valvetrain is whisper-quiet with perfect lash, and the gearbox synchros remain crisp and positive under high-load shifts. We\u2019ve optimized the suspension geometry for neutral turn-in while preserving the torsional rigidity of the factory bushings. Zero parasitic draws, no heat soak issues, and an undercarriage that reflects a meticulous climate-controlled history. This isn't just a driver; it's a precision-engineered investment for the discerning purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
